  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>Intense blue water magically holds its shape-a perfect sphere. The spell DC of any spell cast by Activating this item is 24.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Armor</strong> You gain resistance 5 to water effects and attacks by water creatures.</li>\n<li><strong>Weapon</strong> After you cast a water spell by Activating the <em>droplet</em>, your body becomes mistlike. Until the end of the turn, you can move through enemies' spaces. You can't move through creatures that have the water trait in this way.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-effects.Item.q58ahUEjUzTXffRN]{Effect: Perfect Droplet - Armor (Greater)}</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> Cast a Spell</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You cast <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.eSL5hVT9gXrnRLtd]{Spout}</em>.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> Cast a Spell</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You cast <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.oUDNCArkQTdhllxD]{Aqueous Orb}</em> or <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.RvBlSIJmxiqfCpR9]{Feet to Fins}</em>.</p>"
